    "rules": [
      "Always prefer the combination_mark as the primary logo whenever space and context allow.",
      "Use the logo_mark (icon-only) for avatars, favicons, small spaces, or when the full brand is already established in context.",
      "Maintain clear space equal to the height of the logo mark on all sides for every logo usage.",
      "Approved backgrounds for logos: white, #0A2540 (Invictus Blue), #0E3258. Avoid busy, patterned, or unapproved backgrounds.",
      "Prefer SVG files for all vector work and programmatic generation by agents; use the provided PNGs only for raster needs or quick placement.",
      "Do not alter, stretch, recolor (except using the provided light/dark variants), add effects, or distort any logo.",
      "For organization avatar pages (e.g., Rock RMS), use the brand avatar PNGs at 512×512 px with transparent background where possible."
